{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/CSS/[CSS] flex grow, shrink, basis에 대해/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Yonyas 블로그","author":"Jiyon Lee","siteUrl":"https://yonyas.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"Yonyas/blog-comments"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"jbee"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"13bbcb07-ca3a-5af1-8ba8-379817a94c20","excerpt":"반응형 웹 만들 때 flex 속성들이 헷갈리는 부분이 있어서 정리해본다. 위 코드는 자식태그들에 자동적으로 아래 속성들을 넣는다. flex-grow  : 기본  : 부모의 크기를 다 차지해라. 기본이 row니까 width를 다 차지한다고 생각. 그런데 두번째 child의 컨텐츠 크기가 엄청 크다면? grow를 무시하고 두번째 child가 제일 커진다. 즉 컨텐츠 크기가 중요하다. flex-shrink  : 기본. 줄어들어라. 다른 아이템들과 같게.  : 절대로 줄어들지 마라! flex-basis…","html":"<p>반응형 웹 만들 때 flex 속성들이 헷갈리는 부분이 있어서 정리해본다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>parent<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>child<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Child<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>child<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Child<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>child<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Child<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n.parent { display: flex; }</code></pre></div>\n<p>위 코드는 자식태그들에 자동적으로 아래 속성들을 넣는다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* 자동 속성들 */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.child</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">flex</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0 1 auto<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* 아래와 같다. */</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* max min idealSize 로 외우면 편하다. */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.child</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">flex-grow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* 컨텐츠의 크기만큼 차지해라 */</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">flex-shrink</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* 항상 같은 크기를 차지해라 */</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">flex-basis</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> auto<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* 컨텐츠 크기만큼 차지해라 */</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"flex-grow\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#flex-grow\" aria-label=\"flex grow permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>flex-grow</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">flex-grow: 0;</code> : 기본</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">flex-grow: 1;</code> : 부모의 크기를 다 차지해라. 기본이 row니까 width를 다 차지한다고 생각.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* 다른 아이템의 3배만큼의 크기를 갖는다. */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.child-three</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">flex-grow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 3<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>그런데<br>\n두번째 child의 컨텐츠 크기가 엄청 크다면?<br>\ngrow를 무시하고 두번째 child가 제일 커진다.</p>\n<p>즉 컨텐츠 크기가 중요하다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"flex-shrink\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#flex-shrink\" aria-label=\"flex shrink permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>flex-shrink</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">flex-shrink: 1;</code> : 기본. 줄어들어라. 다른 아이템들과 같게.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">flex-shrink: 0;</code> : 절대로 줄어들지 마라!</p>\n<h3 id=\"flex-basis\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#flex-basis\" aria-label=\"flex basis permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>flex-basis</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">flex-basis: auto;</code> 기본. 이상적 사이즈는 컨텐츠의 사이즈이다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"parent의-크기-전체를-차지하고자-한다면\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#parent%EC%9D%98-%ED%81%AC%EA%B8%B0-%EC%A0%84%EC%B2%B4%EB%A5%BC-%EC%B0%A8%EC%A7%80%ED%95%98%EA%B3%A0%EC%9E%90-%ED%95%9C%EB%8B%A4%EB%A9%B4\" aria-label=\"parent의 크기 전체를 차지하고자 한다면 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>parent의 크기 전체를 차지하고자 한다면?</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-width: 100\">;</code> or <code class=\"language-flex-basis: 100\">;</code> or <code class=\"language-text\">flex-grow: 1;</code><br>\n서로가 영향을 미치기 때문에 단축어로 한번에 사용해주는 것이 한번에 볼 수 있어 좋다.<br>\n참고로 width보다 flex-basis 우선순위가 높다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"코드로-생각해보기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C%EB%A1%9C-%EC%83%9D%EA%B0%81%ED%95%B4%EB%B3%B4%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"코드로 생각해보기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>코드로 생각해보기</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>작은 화면에서는 1000px이 되지 않는다.</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.child-three</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">flex</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0 1 1000px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>basis say : 1000px 너비를 잡도록 노력을 해줘라. 안되면 비율이라도 많이 해줘라.<br>\nshrink say : 줄어들 때 다른애들과 같아지도록 줄어들어라.</p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>1000px에 고정.</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.child-three</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">flex</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0 0 1000px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>shrink say : 절대로 줄지 마라! ==> 1000px로 고정된다. 부모를 넘든말든.</p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>wrap을 한다면 어떨까?</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.parent</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> flex<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">flex-wrap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> wrap<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.child-three</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">flex</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0 0 1000px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>두줄이 되면서 셋째자식이 밑줄로 간다.<br>\nflex는 원래 아이템들을 한줄에 맞추도록 노력하지만 wrap을 하면 같은 공간에 맞지 않으면 한 줄을 더 생성한다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"출처\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B6%9C%EC%B2%98\" aria-label=\"출처 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>출처</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://css-tricks.com/understanding-flex-grow-flex-shrink-and-flex-basis/\">https://css-tricks.com/understanding-flex-grow-flex-shrink-and-flex-basis/</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"[CSS] flex grow, shrink, basis에 대해","date":"July 28, 2021"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/CSS/[CSS] flex grow, shrink, basis에 대해/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/JavaScript/4.미정/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"미정"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/알고리즘/[프로그래머스] 타겟넘버/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[프로그래머스] 타겟넘버 - JS"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["2486386679","3128451518"]}